{"tid":600401,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"收兵嘅女人真係好仆街","createTime":"2018-03-21T09:08:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-22T09:27:24.000Z","uid":172607,"like":41,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"f67f9f03b223a5c4057b037bbbcf70b345c93605","tid":600401,"uid":172607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T09:08:06.000Z","msg":"如果大家當初曖昧過，而個女仔又明知男仔中意佢，但男仔表完白，最後女仔講一句都係覺得大家做朋友好d。然後又繼續約個男仔出黎食個飯見面去街算點？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n呢班女人就係睇中哂毒撚心聲，知道班毒撚仲係對自己有好感，所以得閒就中意撚狗咁撚下佢地，<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 約食飯行街<br />\n<br />\n有人可能會話男女之間都有純友誼，無錯，係有呀，但唔係對一個曾經向你表過嘅異性囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以女人們 如果你地從來無打算同個男仔一齊，麻煩派完好人卡之後就淡出啦，成日聊個男仔去街搏咩？就係享受緊俾人中意嘅感覺 玩弄人地於掌心中囉屌你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7c77155d3b1f63a8727316720e6ab0cc220b68d","tid":600401,"uid":135297,"like":32,"dislike":1,"score":31,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T09:09:53.000Z","msg":"內容大意：樓主發現自己做左兵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22c28b67a3d456ca81deac914e2b87c3be265137","tid":600401,"uid":172607,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T09:11:08.000Z","msg":"見得太多呢種女人，巴打們要企硬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03864e69474496f0e34fbf2b05d9b48e040b70bc","tid":600401,"uid":172607,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b7c77155d3b1f63a8727316720e6ab0cc220b68d","tid":600401,"uid":135297,"like":32,"dislike":1,"score":31,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T09:09:53.000Z","msg":"內容大意：樓主發現自己做左兵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T09:11:59.000Z","msg":"利申：從來無做人隻兵，只係見身邊太多女性朋友會分享呢d事"},{"pid":"2b99afc9faef07ea7ce3e0d